             depos'd, That - Price came to him and ask'd him if his Master would buy such a Horse, and said he was Partner with the Prosecutor, who liv'd in Thames-Street, was gone to Redding, left him to sell that Horse, and to follow him to Redding, to buy Horses, he himself finding Skill, and the Prosecutor Money. That he acquainted his Master with it. 
               <persName id="t17240521-13-person97">
                  William 
                  Villars 
               <interp inst="t17240521-13-person97" type="surname" value="Villars"></interp>
